Firayim Minista Theresa May a wata hira da ta yi da jaridar Sunday Times ta zargi masu sukar shirin ta na ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai da yin wasa da makomar Burtaniya da kuma bata mutuncin kasa.
Firayim Ministan Birtaniya Theresa May ta halarci taron jam'iyyar Conservative Party da aka gudanar a Birmingham, Birtaniya, ranar 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018.
A wata hira da aka yi da shi a shafin farko na jaridar, tsohon sakataren harkokin wajensa Boris Johnson ya yi tir da shirin da ya kira "godiya" na Birtaniya na ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai, inda ya ce bai yi tunanin bukatar Birtaniya da Tarayyar Turai su tara haraji ba.
'Yan sanda sun kama Dighton Simpson a matsayin wanda ake zargi da kisan dan wasan LSU
'Yan sanda sun kama wani da ake zargi da harbin dan wasan kwando na LSU mai shekaru 20 mai suna Wade Sims.
An kama Dighton Simpson, mai shekaru 20, kuma an same shi da laifin kisan kai na mataki na biyu kuma an tsare shi a kurkuku, in ji sashen 'yan sanda na Baton Rouge.
Majiyoyin hukuma sun fitar da bidiyon da ke nuna yadda Sims da Simpson suka yi gardama, kuma 'yan sanda sun ce Sims ya rasa tabarau a lokacin da suka yi faɗa.
Kamfanin WAFB na CBS ya ruwaito cewa 'yan sanda sun gano tabarau a wurin da lamarin ya faru kuma sun ce suna dauke da DNA na Simpson.
Bayan da aka yi wa Simpson tambayoyi, 'yan sanda sun ce ya yarda cewa ya kashe Wade.
An sanya wa mai kare hakkinsa belin dala dubu 350.
Mai binciken yankin Baton Rouge ta Gabas ya fitar da rahoto na farko a ranar Juma'a, wanda ya nuna cewa harbin ya kai ga mutuwarsa, watau harbin da aka yi masa a wuyansa.
Ma'aikatar ta gode wa rundunar 'yan sandan Louisiana da suka bi sahun dan ta'addan, da kuma dakin binciken 'yan sanda na jihar, da kuma jami'ar 'yan sanda ta Kudu da kuma mazauna yankin da suka taimaka wajen gano da kuma kama shi.
Shugaban Kwalejin Wasanni na LSU Joe Alleva ya gode wa hukumomin tsaro saboda himma da kuma bin hanyar adalci.
Sims yana da shekara 20.
Baton Ruja, dan wasan gaba mai tsayi 6ft 6in, ya girma, mahaifinsa kuma ya buga kwando a LSU.
A kakar da ta gabata, ya ci gaba da samun maki 5.6 da kuma kwallaye 2.6.
A safiyar Juma'a, kocin kwando na LSU, Will Wade, ya ce kungiyar ta yi kasala kuma ta yi sanyin gwiwa game da mutuwar Wade.
"Kina damuwa da wannan abu kullum", in ji Wade.
