Daruruwan 'yan adawa da Erdogan, da yawancinsu Kurdawa, sun yi ta yin zanga-zangar adawa da manufofin Erdogan da kuma shawarar da gwamnatin Jamus ta yanke na karbarsa.
Wannan baƙo da wasu Jamusawa suka ɗaukaka a matsayin mai girma, wasu kuma suka ɗaukaka shi a matsayin mai iko, ya zama sanadin jayayya tsakanin ɓangarorin biyu.
