Girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia sun kashe daruruwan mutane, kuma adadin wadanda suka mutu na karuwa
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu yayin da manyan raƙuman ruwa suka yi taho da raƙuman ruwa a tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia, inda mutane da dama suka nitse, in ji jami'an a ranar Asabar.
Ruwa mai tsayi mita shida (18 feet) ya buge bakin teku lokacin da aka rufe shinge, kuma daruruwan mutane sun taru a ranar Jumma'a don yin biki a bakin rairayin bakin teku a cikin garin Palo, inda mutane da yawa suka mutu kuma raƙuman ruwa suka lalata duk wanda ke kan hanya.
Tsunami ya faru ne bayan girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5.
Mutanen da ke kan rairayin bakin teku suna gudanar da ayyukansu a lokacin da ake fuskantar barazanar tsunami kuma ba su gudu ba nan da nan kuma sun mutu,  in ji Sutopo Purvo Nugroho, mai magana da yawun Hukumar Kula da Bala'in Bala'i ta Indonesia (BNPB) a wani taron tattaunawa a Jakarta.
 Tsunami bai zo da kansa ba, ya kwashe motoci, motoci, gidaje, ya buge kowa a cikin ƙasa,  in ji Nugroho, kuma ya kara da cewa tsunami ya motsa a cikin teku mai zurfi da saurin mil 497 a kowace awa (800 km / h) kafin ya buga layin gabar teku.
"Wasu sun tsere wa tsunami, wasu sun hau bishiyoyi, suka tsira", in ji shi.
An kwashe mutane kusan 16,700 zuwa cibiyoyi 24 a cikin garin Palu.
Hotunan iska da hukumar ta bayar sun nuna cewa gine-gine da shagunan da dama sun rushe, gadaje sun lalace kuma an lalata su, kuma masallaci ya cika da ruwa.
A ranar Asabar ne aka ga ƙanƙara a bakin kogin.
An ji girgizar kasa a yankin da ke da mazaunan mutane miliyan 2.4.
Hukumar Indonesiya ta kimantawa da amfani da fasaha (BPPT) ta ruwaito cewa, a cikin sanarwar da ta fitar, an samu karfin da girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta fitar a ranar Juma'a, wanda ya ninka na bam din nukiliya da aka jefa a Hiroshima a lokacin yakin duniya na biyu sau 200.
An ce, wurin da birnin yake a ƙarshen wani dogon kwari mai zurfi, ya sa tsunami ya yi yawa.
Nugroho ya bayyana lalacewar a matsayin "mai girma" kuma ya ce dubban gidaje, asibitoci, cibiyoyin kasuwanci da otal-otal sun lalace.
Ya ce an gano gawarwakin wasu daga cikin wadanda aka kashe a karkashin rushewar gine-gine, kuma mutane 540 sun ji rauni, kuma 29 sun bace.
