Menene muhimmancin bikin Global Citizen kuma ya taimaka wajen rage talauci?
A wannan Asabar, birnin New York zai karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen, wani biki na shekara-shekara wanda ke nuna cewa yana da babbar manufa ta kawar da talauci a duniya, tare da halartar manyan taurari masu tasiri a cikin al'umma.
A bikin cika shekaru bakwai da kafuwar bikin Global Citizen, dubun dubatar mutane za su halarci babban filin Central Park ba wai kawai don kallon taurari kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Sean Mendes ba, amma kuma don wayar da kan jama'a game da kawar da talauci a duniya nan da shekarar 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012 ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wani shiri na kungiyar kare hakkin bil adama ta duniya da ke neman kawar da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan masu fafutukar yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta (ba tare da son siyan tikitin VIP ba, ba shakka) masu sauraro dole ne su yi aiki mai mahimmanci ko ayyuka masu mahimmanci waɗanda ke haɓaka wayar da kan jama'a game da manufar kawar da talauci, ko rubuta wasiƙa ga shugaban duniya, ko yin kira.
Amma, da yake an rage shekara 12 kawai kafin a cimma burin, yaya nasarar Global Citizen take?
Shin hanyar da ta dace don samar da kyauta ga jama'a ita ce ta hanyar yin kira ga jama'a suyi aiki, ko kuma wani misali na wannan "clictivism" - imani cewa mutane suna yin canji ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takarda kan layi ko kuma yin tweet?
A cewar Global Citizen, tun shekarar 2011 kungiyar ta shirya fiye da abubuwa miliyan 19 tare da taimakon masu goyon baya don dalilai daban-daban.
A cewarsu, wadannan abubuwan sun karfafawa shugabannin duniya gwiwa wajen bayyana kudade da bukatun da suka kai dala biliyan 37 da zasu shafi rayuwar mutane sama da biliyan 2.25 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon shekarar 2018, kungiyar ta yi rahoton ayyuka 390 da aka sanar da su, wadanda suka haifar da abubuwan da aka shirya, kuma daga cikinsu an tara ko kuma kashe akalla dala biliyan 10.
Ƙungiyar ta bayyana cewa, albarkatun da aka samar sun shafi rayukan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Daya daga cikin manyan ayyukan shine The Power of Nutrition, wani haɗin gwiwar masu saka hannun jari na Burtaniya da masu zartarwa waɗanda suka yi alkawarin ba da dala miliyan 35 ga Rwanda don magance matsalar karancin abinci a yankin bayan sun tattara tweets 4,700 a madadin Global Citizens.
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da agaji, gwamnatocin kasa da kuma Global Citizens, za mu iya kawo karshen rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki", in ji Tracey Ullman, jakadan The Power of Nutrition, a wani taron jama'a a watan Afrilu na shekarar 2018 a London.
Bugu da kari, a cewar kungiyar, an shirya fiye da ayyuka 5,000 a Burtaniya da suka shafi inganta ingancin abinci ga mata da yara, kuma gwamnati ta sanar da kudade ga shirin The Power of Nutrition wanda ya shafi kusan mata da yara miliyan biyar.
A cikin jerin sunayen da suka yi a shafin su na intanet, sun yi tambaya: Me ya sa muke da tabbacin cewa za mu yi nasara a yaki da talauci?
Global citizen ya amsa, "Zai zama hanya mai tsawo da wahala, kuma za mu iya yin kasa da kasa a wasu lokuta".
Amma kamar yadda aka yi a cikin 'yancin jama'a da kuma na 'yanci, za mu yi nasara domin idan muka hada kai, za mu fi karfi.
A wannan shekarar, Deborah-Lee Ferness da Hugh Jackman za su yi wasan kwaikwayon a New York City, wanda ya kunshi Janet Jackson, Wickend, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Monet.
