An sake jinkirta sabon jirgin ruwan Jamus
A shekarar 2014 ne aka fara amfani da sabon fasalin jirgin ruwan sojin Jamus don maye gurbin jiragen ruwa na yakin basasa, wanda aka yi amfani da shi a lokacin yakin basasa, duk da haka, a cewar kafofin watsa labarai na gida, ba za a kawo su ba har sai a kalla shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da farashin isarwa.
An jinkirta fara aiki da babban jirgin ruwa na Rhineland-Pfalz, wanda zai kasance cikin sabbin jiragen ruwa a cikin layin Baden-Württemberg, zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019, jaridar Die Zeit ta ruwaito ta danganta da bayanin da wani jami'in soji ya bayar.
Ya kamata a ba da jirgin ruwan a cikin 2014, duk da haka, matsalolin da suka taso bayan isar da jirgin sun shafi makomar wannan babban aikin.
Jiragen ruwa hudu na Lines Baden-Württemberg da aka ba da umarnin a cikin 2007 za su maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Lines Bremen.
An san cewa suna da makamai masu linzami masu ƙarfi, da makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami da yawa, da kuma fasahohin da ba a iya gani kamar ƙaramin radar, infrared da siginar sauti.
Sauran muhimman ayyuka na iya kasancewa a cikin jerin tsawon lokacin aiki, wato, yiwuwar wadatar da jiragen ruwa na karshe da aka aika daga cikin tashar jiragen ruwa har zuwa shekaru biyu.
Duk da haka, jinkiri na yau da kullun yana nufin cewa mafi kyawun jiragen ruwa na zamani waɗanda aka yi niyya don ba da damar Jamus don yin hasashen wutar lantarki a ƙasashen waje za su tsufa ba tare da an fara su ba, Die Zeit ta lura.
Frigate F125 da ya lalace ya shiga jerin labarai na harbi lokacin da rundunar sojin ruwan Jamus ta ƙi shigar da jirgin cikin aiki a shekarar da ta gabata kuma ta mayar da shi ga kamfanin Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan abu ne da ba a taɓa yi ba a tarihin jiragen ruwa, inda rundunar jiragen ruwa ke mayar da jirgin bayan an kawo shi.
Babu cikakken bayani game da dalilan da suka sa aka mayar da jirgin, duk da haka, kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun yi magana game da wasu "ƙwarewar software da na'urori" waɗanda suka sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani a lokacin aikin soja.
Rashin inganci a cikin software yana da mahimmanci, saboda jiragen ruwa a kan layin Baden-Württemberg suna da ƙungiyoyi na kimanin 120 na matuƙan ruwa, wanda shine rabin rabin tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Bugu da ƙari, an gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyi sosai, wanda ke nufin cewa nauyin ya rage yawan aikin jirgin kuma ya iyakance damar da sojojin ruwa ke da shi na yin ƙarin cigaba a nan gaba.
Rhineland-Pfalz mai nauyin tan 7000 an yi la'akari da shi sau biyu fiye da irin wannan nau'in jiragen ruwa da Jamusawa suka yi amfani da su a lokacin yakin duniya na biyu.
Kudin wannan aikin, ban da matsalar kayan aiki, tare da farashin horar da ƙungiyar, ya zama batun da ake jayayya.
Ya ce, ya kai matakin da ya fi ban mamaki, wato daga Euro biliyan 2.2 zuwa Euro biliyan 3.1 (dala biliyan 3.6).
Bayan gargadi game da raguwar sojojin Jamus, batun kama sabbin jirage masu saukar ungulu yana da matukar muhimmanci a yau.
A farkon wannan shekarar, shugaban kwamitin tsaron majalisar dokoki na Jamus Hans-Peter Bartels ya ce "za a kusan gama yawan jiragen ruwa masu aiki da ke cikin rundunar soji".
Sheneunik ya ce batun ya kara zama da damuwa saboda an dakatar da tsofaffin jiragen ruwa kuma ba a kawo masu maye gurbin su ba.
Ya yi korafin cewa babu wani daga cikin jiragen ruwa na Baden-Württemberg da aka ba da shi ga rundunar sojan ruwa.
