Amurka ta rage takunkumin da ta yanke wa El Salvador saboda goyon bayan da take baiwa China
'Yan diplomasiyar sun lura cewa Jamhuriyar Dominica da Panama sun amince da Beijing tare da ɗan ƙin yarda daga Washington.
A watan Yunin 2017, Mista Trump ya yi wata ganawa da shugaban Panama Juan Carlos Valera, kuma ya yi zaman otel a Panama, har sai abokan aikinsa suka kori ƙungiyar gudanarwa ta Trump Organization.
A cikin wata sanarwa da aka fitar a farkon wannan watan, sakataren ma'aikatar harkokin wajen kasar, Heather Nauert, ta ce, a daidai da hukuncin da aka yanke na daina amincewa da Taiwan, jami'an ma'aikatar harkokin wajen kasar sun yanke shawarar mayar da shugabannin diflomasiyar Amurka daga El Salvador, Jamhuriyar Dominica da Panama.
Koyaya, an sanya tara ne kawai a kan El Salvador a cikin 2017, wanda ya karɓi dala miliyan 140 daga Amurka don rage amfani da miyagun ƙwayoyi, ci gaba da tattalin arziƙi da tallafi ga ƙasar.
Babu shakka, tarar da ake son a yi wa kasar ta tsakiya ta Amurka, wadda ke da yawan rashin aikin yi da kuma kisan kai, da rage tallafin kuɗi da kuma takunkumin ba da biza, zai yi muni sosai.
A yayin da ake ci gaba da gudanar da taron na cikin gida, shugabannin Arewacin Amurka da na Amurka ta Tsakiya sun jinkirta taron koli na tsaro da bunkasa tattalin arziki da aka yi a bara don gudanar da irin wannan taron, wanda aka yi la'akari da shi a matsayin ci gaba a kan hana baƙi zuwa Amurka.
A tsakiyar watan Satumba, duk da haka, manyan shugabannin sun nuna cikakken goyon baya ga taron da za a yi a gaba, wanda a sakamakon haka, ya nuna cewa suna son a dakatar da takunkumin da aka kafa wa El Salvador.
A cewar jami'an diflomasiyya, mataimakin shugaban kasa Mike Pence na shirin tattauna batun samar da kujeru a majalisar dattawa a wani taro da za a yi a tsakiyar watan Oktoba.
